Name:           glslang
Version:        11.13.0
Release:        2%{?dist}
Summary:        OpenGL and OpenGL ES shader front end and validator
License:        BSD and GPLv3+ and ASL 2.0
URL:            https://github.com/KhronosGroup/glslang
Group:          Development/Tools
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
